Class EvaluateContextState

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.EvaluateContextState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EvaluateContext

    public class EvaluateContextState
extends java.lang.Object
implements EvaluateContext
    Information required to evaluate an expression: a State object. This is basically an array of Objects, indexed according to a model file. Optionally values for constants can also be supplied.
